/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b2b9d270e6305f27d354ce8c821a08f9951908","tid":1635081,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9079a67d92f1465e2ad8d3a001b534a81ec9292","tid":1635081,"uid":113975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲幫個的士佬兜 話部車有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"已經同佢無討論空間<br />\n真係好撚可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8950128b3ae531861feb62746d38b9456419ca8","tid":1635081,"uid":191145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb9f521df5340d7e7a0c99934b1699a0ceb210aa","tid":1635081,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">家母係一隻不折不扣 不問世事既港豬<br />\n自6月反送中運動開始<br />\n其實佢乜撚都唔知<br />\n反送中 五大訴求係乜佢都唔會講得出<br />\n但就日日打開cctvb 83台睇新聞扮關心時事<br />\n（有試過轉台轉32 但過一陣佢就自己轉去83台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n到近日cctvb只大篇幅報導香港經濟蕭條、各位手足四圍幫中資黨鐵裝修<br />\n佢就日日喺屋企發癲<br />\n話我地班人痴線 搞亂香港<br />\n我試過解釋俾佢聽我地年輕人究竟爭取緊啲乜<br />\n但佢完全聽唔入耳<br />\n我已經放棄左爭取佢由藍轉黃<br />\n事關佢有個娘家whatsapp group日撚日幫佢洗腦<br />\n入面全撚部都係藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日撚日都圍爐互sd屈穎姸 建制狗同藍絲既偉大言論同假片假相<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚灰心<br />\n點解最親既人可以咁無知<br />\n我心痛既係點解由細到大教我明辨是非、對錯既人<br />\n竟然會係一個腦殘既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次發完夢返屋企<br />\n我都會匿埋喺房喊<br />\n因為我覺得不被親人理解真係好撚無奈同心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺度諗<br />\n如果琴日係我俾廢老藍絲撞斷左對腳<br />\n佢係咪都唔會可憐我<br />\n只會覺得係自己個女抵死行出街俾車撞？<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多巴絲屋企氣氛都唔太和諧<br />\n所以我唯有上黎搵你地圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後<br />\nCCTVB的確係邪惡軸心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地成個新聞部既人仲未有報應只係時辰未到咋我屌你地老母</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:00:29.000Z","msg":"我老母係深藍近紅 721 831對電視嗌打得好<br />\n我一路無打算說服佢 因為我知說黎哂L氣<br />\n所以斬相處得幾唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次佢話班友又黎搞事啦 （我住催淚彈旺區）<br />\n我都會好興奮咁叫佢：「拿拿聲拎刀落去斬人啦你。去啦去啦！」佢每次都話我痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我就補多句：「唔斬就收皮啦，無L用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n如是者 有講有笑<br />\n但有一次佢同佢d on9 fd傾電話話人「曱甴」<br />\n我個下堅屌佢 仲掌鳩佢把口 打左場交<br />\n依排冷戰中 未完全好返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8c134de9eb676f3473390a6758944d02493e78","tid":1635081,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87824679ca9bde1541de73ba7163cd2badeecfcb","tid":1635081,"uid":207347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"老豆深藍 爺爺直頭紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放棄再同佢地傾政治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"喺屋企好難過<br />\n唔想返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36898fdb1e0ceab2163db1c2a626c749948a1d51","tid":1635081,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c912331832f66e651f4a55f19fb9f70d11adb67","tid":16